summary: Debating on whether or not to go see "Captain Marvel" for a third time tonight. (Due to a weird work schedule this week I am off...
body:
Debating on whether or not to go see “Captain Marvel” for a third time tonight. (Due to a weird work schedule this week I am off tonight, and working my usual days off.)

On one hand, I have already seen it twice, I’ve got several projects to do around my apartment, and I do have a bunch of movies and TV seadons borrowed from the library I need to watch.

On the other hand, I do really like it, and no matter how well it’s doing at the box office, it can always use more support, since box office numbers are really the only things those stupid suits in hollywood really look at. And if we wanna see more movies like it in the future, which I do, it needs to have the numbers pumped up.

Decisions, decisions, decisions.

Thoughts/opinions/suggestions?
